      <title>'We are being driven from the land' - after a massacre, a Nigerian village buries its dead</title>
      <author>Emmanuel Akinwotu</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/26/nx-s1-5471472/we-are-being-driven-from-the-land-after-a-massacre-a-nigerian-village-buries-its-dead</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/07/26/nx-s1-5471472/we-are-being-driven-from-the-land-after-a-massacre-a-nigerian-village-buries-its-dead</comments>
